http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Power-shutdown-in-Shivamogga-today/article13983607.ece

There will be no power supply in Machenahalli, Bidire, Nidige, Otighatta, Siddaragudi, Harekatte, Sogane, Achari Camp, Hosur, Reddy Camp, Dummalli, Sugar Colony, Jayanti, K.S.R.P. Colony, Navule-Basapura, Hathikatte, Honnavile, Amaravathi Camp, Shettyhalli, Hale Shettyhalli, Gudrakoppa, Mattighatta, Malenahalli and surrounding villages on January 6 between 9 a.m. and 6 p.m. owing to the installation of fire protection system at the power distribution centre in Machenahalli.AppealIn a press release issued here on Tuesday, Assistant Executive Engineer of the Mangalore Electricity Supply Company has requested he public to cooperate.